## Performance

| Metric | Raw Code | TLDR | Improvement |
|--------|----------|------|-------------|
| Tokens for function context | 21,000 | 175 | **99% savings** |
| Tokens for codebase overview | 104,000 | 12,000 | **89% savings** |
| Query latency (daemon) | 30s | 100ms | **300x faster** |

